{"tid":454342,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛夫雲收死亡恐嚇：忍無可忍","createTime":"2017-11-01T04:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T16:34:32.000Z","uid":333,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"dad3577bfcb816131fb8107d2736cd0774024792","tid":454342,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=xuRX9uJAygzHR0L88SaOr49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7ddd2ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦後衛洛夫雲季初表現慘不忍睹，受批評之餘甚至收到網民死亡恐嚇。<br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞國腳洛夫雲（Dejan Lovren）自從由修咸頓加盟利物浦後，似乎沒過好日子，以1:4大敗給熱刺後，遭到鋪天蓋地的網上惡評。該名紅軍守將透過Instagram，告訴球迷收到死亡恐嚇，相信是疑似利迷寫道：「你這個克羅地亞廢柴，我會殺晒你全家人。」<br />\n<br />\n洛夫雲目前與妻子Anita還有兩名子女居住在利物浦，他回應道：「我從來不介意別人插我，但禍不及家人，士可殺、不可辱，我已忍無可忍，這些言論非常噁心。」<br />\n<br />\n上輪英超，紅軍擊敗哈特斯菲爾德，洛夫雲熱身後並沒被派上陣，他早前自爆曾要服食5粒止痛丸才能比賽。"},{"pid":"32fdd2347d7718dee27be7d81d4083799515aa55","tid":454342,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42cfd226e777cbf7b27d87e29aa9e83cd034fbb","tid":454342,"uid":18646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  利狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ef7fa82b7e351010fc37f6c91e9e990214290f","tid":454342,"uid":21896,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"口口聲you will never walk alone,但踢得差就要死全家😅"},{"pid":"6d02af6f6d81f3224822b8fe8f67676ca760af70","tid":454342,"uid":3747,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"說好的YNWA呢？"},{"pid":"326323ab354f37ffcf2d6f2b171868dcafd9da09","tid":454342,"uid":18646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>口口聲you will 